content.rendered: “My Personal Annual Birthday Forecast” does not give you exact dates for decision-making in the coming year. That is not the purpose of the solar return chart.  If you are seeking dates to initiate actions in your personal and professional life, please consult Susan Miller’s monthly forecasts for both your Sun sign and Rising sign at the beginning of each month at AstrologyZone Susan’s advice is exclusive, original and FREE.
